              Funny
              <img src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/emoticon/72x72/1f602.png" alt="Funny"><span class="num">0</span></div><div class="btn-reaction js-btn-reaction confusing ga-click" data-ga-click-type="review-anime-reaction-confusing" data-id="168223" data-val="4" data-more="false" style="display: none;">
              Confusing
