              <img src="https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/emoticon/72x72/1f928.png" alt="Confusing"><span class="num">0</span></div><div class="btn-reaction js-btn-reaction informative ga-click" data-ga-click-type="review-anime-reaction-informative" data-id="104793" data-val="5" data-more="true" style="display: none;">
